---
title: Dairy Free Risotto (v) with Butternut, Sage, Caramelised Onion and Hazelnuts
description: We love Risotto with Butternut & Sage and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dairy-free-risotto-438aac2c-dbfd1c7b.jpg
